msgstr ":ref:`ConsideraĂ§Ă”es de seguranĂ§a sobre SSL/TLS <ssl-security>`"

#: ../../library/asyncio-eventloop.rst:482
msgid ""
"*server_hostname* sets or overrides the hostname that the target server's "
